              "title": "zitten + te + infinitive",
              "body": "'Zaten te kwebbelen' = were chattering (while seated). This is the 'sitting' progressive. Dutch uses the posture verb (zitten/staan/liggen/lopen) + te + infinitive to describe ongoing actions."
